{"tid":755182,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[正能量]請入嚟分享工作上嘅滿足感","createTime":"2018-07-25T04:02:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-25T14:30:31.000Z","uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6f81b54fc8fc35f5d3680f9c04cbcb87955195a4","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"我係freshgrad，等緊開工。<br />\n見到有唔少人喺其他post留言話番工好灰好冇意義。<br />\n想聽下一啲正面嘅經歷，等大家都可以有所啟發。<br />\n<br />\n呢幅圖係上網揾嘅，當你做緊嘅事，符合晒四個條件，嗰件事就係你嘅人生意義。如果只係符合其中某啲條件，咁就係passion, mission, profession 或 vocation。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/113644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F113644_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=af5ae84d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n留言可以從嗰四項條件分享下你嘅工作，例如有啲咩令你享受呢份工作。如果有試過唔同嘅工作，都可以分享下轉工嘅過程係點。<br />\n<br />\n另外都可以分享下你覺得點解份工滿足唔到你，有咩阻住你去做一份滿足到你嘅工。<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多，大家諗到咩就講咩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14aba734f4687ee39ac4c73933b0b2f711d582c6","tid":755182,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"放工。"},{"pid":"8f1696f72a4d7fa7e61ecafda72c978a696af7e5","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aba734f4687ee39ac4c73933b0b2f711d582c6","tid":755182,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"放工。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"放工會做啲咩？"},{"pid":"38a50333e1dfdc3492fe4f828efb3e2e438b6bf1","tid":755182,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f1696f72a4d7fa7e61ecafda72c978a696af7e5","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aba734f4687ee39ac4c73933b0b2f711d582c6","tid":755182,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"放工。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"放工會做啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"煲劇，食飯，訓覺，等死<br />\n利申：返咗2年半工"},{"pid":"bf22b276e55e77acd30ceaa9a59506763c1cb7fb","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38a50333e1dfdc3492fe4f828efb3e2e438b6bf1","tid":755182,"uid":113929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f1696f72a4d7fa7e61ecafda72c978a696af7e5","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14aba734f4687ee39ac4c73933b0b2f711d582c6","tid":755182,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"放工。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"放工會做啲咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"煲劇，食飯，訓覺，等死<br />\n利申：返咗2年半工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"放工應該已經唔想用腦，惟有回氣聽日再番工。。除非鍾意做嗰樣嘢鍾意到唔覺攰，或者嗰樣嘢會帶嚟滿足感"},{"pid":"7f76c9ad3711dfa86f2a05f771fcc25040144c42","tid":755182,"uid":176598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T14:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/25/223028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F25%2F223028_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1261ceda&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}